{"tid":491230,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登戰報】港股牛定熊 估吓連登網友點睇？","createTime":"2017-12-06T10:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T10:24:24.000Z","uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43ad39d63b7bc21c5c491295d4693399163cf790","tid":491230,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:02:51.000Z","msg":"今日港股一度大跌471點，今年升得多嘅吉利（175）、舜宇（2382）、瑞聲（2018）齊齊成為提款對象，急挫7%。有連登網友關心大市仲係咪牛市，估吓佢哋點睇？<br />\n開post的「有智慧不如趁勢」問：「究竟而家股市處於咩階段？」佢自己先答，認為未見雞犬升天狀態，冇大上大落過，感覺出年仲係大升市。有人回應：「3萬跌1500點好少咋喎」、「牛三前大震倉」、「跌完又升返啦」、「似上年，死完、又正常」、「每年升到咁上下，總會有調整，上山都要回下氣啦」，只有兩位網友話係熊一。換言之，有留言的連登網友，幾乎一面倒睇港股仲有得升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171206/57547190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57547190&d=6ELBg8tlbAmHu5TpQmoco9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=06f2f35d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57547190&h=440ce3e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171206/57547190</a>"},{"pid":"a4fdaeace8d9cb5c29f64e2fa42b23c4241ea313","tid":491230,"uid":116718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:04:20.000Z","msg":"新聞真係易寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c415d23be65416d168e3cf93d4242cd6354f7cea","tid":491230,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:12:55.000Z","msg":"咁都叫新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9ee67d1616eb6656d7a7323df4f72ed215a385","tid":491230,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"馬英狗看錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  連登班估神都好寫"}]}